data.description: NEW Price Improvement! Orange City - With a little TLC this 3 bedroom 2 bath ranch can be turned into a gem. This house offers a split plan with master bedroom on one side and the other two bedrooms on the other side of the house. The kitchen and family room are the heart of the house. The kitchen opens on the family room, ideal to entertain and not miss a beat. Ceramic tile and laminate flooring for easy maintenance. The property is fenced and has a 2-car garage. Located in a quiet neighborhood with easy access to I-4. Close to clinics, restaurants and shopping.
